/**
 * @defgroup selection_module Selection Module
 * @ingroup modules_group
 * @brief Event selection criteria.
 *
 * @section selection_overview Overview
 *
 * The Selection module provides the @ref selection_template class for
 * implementing event selection criteria.
 *
 * @section selection_usage_mod Usage
 *
 * To create a custom selection:
 *
 * 1. Subclass @ref selection_template
 * 2. Override the selection method
 * 3. Return true for events that pass the selection
 *
 * @section selection_chaining_mod Selection Chaining
 *
 * Multiple selections can be combined:
 *
 * - Sequential (AND logic)
 * - Named selections for cutflow analysis
 *
 * @see selection_template
 */

/**
 * @defgroup structs_module Structs Module
 * @ingroup modules_group
 * @brief Core data structures and type definitions.
 *
 * @section structs_overview Overview
 *
 * The Structs module contains fundamental data structures used throughout
 * the framework.
 *
 * @section structs_types Types
 *
 * Key structures include:
 *
 * - @ref settings_t: Analysis configuration
 * - @ref event_t: Event data container
 * - @ref graph_t: Graph data structure (see @ref graph_module)
 * - @ref folds_t: K-fold cross-validation data
 * - @ref optimizer_params_t: Optimizer configuration
 * - @ref model_report: Training progress reports
 *
 * @section structs_property_mod Property System
 *
 * The module includes a property system (`cproperty`) for:
 *
 * - Type-safe getters and setters
 * - Lazy evaluation
 * - Python binding support
 */

